## ğŸ“‹ Overview

**Brain Tumor Detector & Classifier** is a web-based deep learning application that classifies brain MRI scans into four categories using a pre-trained convolutional neural network.

**Tumor Classes:**
- Glioma Tumor
- Meningioma Tumor
- Pituitary Tumor
- No Tumor (Healthy Scan)

**Tech Used:** Python, Flask, TensorFlow/Keras, OpenCV  
**Model:** VGG16 (Transfer Learning)  
**Purpose:** Educational & Research Use Only  

---

